data.title: Alice in Wonderland Birthday Party Capri Sun Label – Editable
data.meta_description: Get this Alice in Wonderland Birthday Party Capri Sun Label Editable Download and customize your fabulous party. Other Alice in Wonderland Labels are available too.
data.text:
If you are having a Alice in Wonderland, Tea Party, Garden party of whimsical themed event or party, make it the best and customize your event with this editable Capri Sun Label. This is a EDITABLE digital download that you print at home or send to a printer after inserting text such as a name. Once you download the file, you can insert text on the PDF or PNG file from any editing application/service such as Canva.com (recommended and it is free and easy to use). You could also insert text using any image editor, MS Word, PhotoscapeX (also free), Adobe PDF Editor, etc. For Canva.com, you just create a free account and start editing.

Please note that no physical product is mailed and this is a download.

Upon purchase, you will receive an email with a a link that has a PDF and PNG download(s). Then open the files into an application that has editing and type whatever you want. Enlarge the file for easier editing. The images and design can not be edited, you can only add text (like the name, date, etc.). You can add the text in any font and/or color. Then print on 8.5 x 11 inch Glossy Inkjet or Laser Sticker Paper (30-32 lb), waterproof paper, or regular white 65 lb card stock. If printing at home, make sure your printer is set on the best quality setting and prints to “actual size”. You may need to ignore margin settings as well. Colors tend to be lighter on gloss paper unless you adjust the settings to the type of paper you are using and set to highest quality.

Please note that this is a download that you print on your own or send to a printer company. No physical product is mailed. Download is sent immediately to your email with link(s) upon receipt of payment. Download is PDF and PNG file(s).

NOTE: ****Major Gates Logo WaterMark is NOT included on purchased downloads.****

Recommended items needed to assemble Capri Sun Labels (these items are not included with this purchase).

-Sharp scissors

-Regular glue stick (if using card stock)

-Color printer

-Paper of choice

-Capri Sun

Cut off any white trim and peel off the backing of the sticker paper. If using regular card stock, apply glue on the back and place on the Capri Sun.

This Download includes the following:

*Capri Sun Label (Editable) blank – 4 per page 8.5″ x 11″ in PNG and PDF

This is a download and no physical product is mailed. Please contact me if you have any issues with your download.

Please visit my shop for matching items.

Products made and labeled by Major Gates are trademarked. By purchasing this item(s), you agree to not distribute or resell the file(s) contained in this download. These are for non-commercial, personal use only. By purchasing, you are agreeing this is for personal use only and will not be resold for any reason.

Please note that colors may vary depending on your printer, ink, and/or choice of paper. Please set printer to best quality settings for best results. Major Gates is not responsible for color variations and there will be no refunds if you experience color variations once printed.
